data.description: Stunning home with impressive 18 foot ceilings, boasting an open floor plan that seamlessly flows from the granite countered kitchen to the spacious living areas.  This home features a dedicated office space near the entrance, and an inviting game room for leisure.  Primary bedroom is on the main floor with dual vanities in the bathroom. Each bedroom has walk in closets. Located in a secure gated community with access to two neighborhood pools offering comfort and recreation. VA assumable loan available at 4.75%. Schedule a showing today!
